{"tid":312511,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"寸習總唔敢放曉波 沙膽網民WeChat一句話被拘7日","createTime":"2017-07-07T13:43:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-08T10:45:37.000Z","uid":1065,"like":6,"dislike":54,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0178af9d2521f8df04f46d0049f9f34b484a6ded","tid":312511,"uid":1065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T13:43:07.000Z","msg":"習近平和劉曉波兩個敏感詞都中！昨日有內地民眾因在微信同學群組中的一句話，被拘留7天。<br />\n<br />\n「釋放劉xiao波，習包子還能安心訪港？」張家界居民敬迎忠因6月30日發在微信中學同學群組的這一句話，被公安定位偵查拘捕，昨日遭以侮辱黨國領導人為由，處以行政拘留7天的處罰。家屬將治安拘留通知書發上網，感覺委屈。　<br />\n<br />\n綜合報道<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56923946&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170707\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56923946%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170707&d=WTAKADb%2Fboub4MpF4uRsB8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=bda85032\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56923946%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170707&h=997e6bba\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56923946&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170707</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://vignette3.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/5/5f/China_human_rights.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvignette3.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F5%2F5f%2FChina_human_rights.jpg&h=b33398ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a9b7227f42aaf1e479c9a205230a60b6b3584fc9","tid":312511,"uid":71257,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T13:54:31.000Z","msg":"習包子死全家"},{"pid":"c31194c2af11967e35a5fe121fc93f0996036200","tid":312511,"uid":15815,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T14:05:15.000Z","msg":"中國共產黨&hellip;&hellip;屌屎忽！屌咗八十幾年，全國鳩頭犯有雞姦死罪！"},{"pid":"7e625b3f7a277e90eb3d6829b65d676601197002","tid":312511,"uid"